Package: dmart
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: dmart <admin@dmart.cc>
Depends: jq
Homepage: https://github.com/edraj/csdmart
Description: dmart - Unified Data Platform (REST API server + CLI)
 dmart is a unified data platform providing a REST API backed by PostgreSQL.
 This package includes the native AOT server binary, the CLI client tool,
 built-in plugin configurations, and a systemd service unit.
 .
 The binary is self-contained (NativeAOT publish, no .NET runtime
 dependency). Built against Debian 12's glibc (2.36) - runs on Debian 12+,
 Ubuntu 22.04+, and any glibc 2.36+ system. Older targets require building
 from source on the target distro.
